ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"same<br />\n背 心口 膊頭都有<br />\n好彩係男 不過唔敢除衫。。。"},{"pid":"95adb61bc157a2b9b5b75a4f4266131edb5e9f09","tid":305841,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:35:29.000Z","msg":"個隻背粒消有冇用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5315b319e3f48654dc5a09d1a06b6cd8175f2f","tid":305841,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"以前青春期好多<br />\n係用左松焦油梘沖涼先受控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600f26d10406bee58ea5b2551bd841a6fbb4c3de","tid":305841,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"不如諗下方法解決？ 我都有依個問題"},{"pid":"f35c9f7033838738116fe8743b5b7af57f467620","tid":305841,"uid":53187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>same<br />\n背 心口 膊頭都有<br />\n好彩係男 不過唔敢除衫。。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我膊頭都有 不過小"},{"pid":"e177693ebe8e39786b87187a662553c1c8a06fa0","tid":305841,"uid":53187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:46:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個隻背粒消有冇用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未用過 我用過茶樹"},{"pid":"d228b8af7229ba4d42334361fa6997a814d0bf50","tid":305841,"uid":53187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如諗下方法解決？ 我都有依個問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我google睇過好多有關既資料 我好sure我係濕熱底 好多野都唔可以食 但同時又食緊冇戒到 例如辣野 煎炸野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   之後雞同豬都唔可以食 我第一眼睇到 心諗 唔撚係呀 咩都唔可以食 你叫我點做 番工已經辛苦 連自己鍾意食既都唔得 人生有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f2a0c16c5e22fa18f4c3b323435be0edd6d6e2","tid":305841,"uid":2836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如諗下方法解決？ 我都有依個問題</blockquote><br />\n我試過既方法：<br />\n1.用松焦油梘-&gt; 好左少少 但都會繼續生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  用左一舊就冇繼續用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.宜家用凍水沖涼 之前沖開熱水  貌似又係好左少少 但都係會生下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 啱啱開始試用日本果隻專for 洗背既番梘 未知會唔會好有效<br />\n<br />\n暫時既結論：發覺啲方法好似都係舒緩多 點都係會生下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f94264a7ad8b9e998cab6f5b3ab2306bd75741","tid":305841,"uid":53187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如諗下方法解決？ 我都有依個問題</blockquote><br />\n我試過既方法：<br />\n1.用松焦油梘-&gt; 好左少少 但都會繼續生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  用左一舊就冇繼續用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.宜家用凍水沖涼 之前沖開熱水  貌似又係好左少少 但都係會生下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 啱啱開始試用日本果隻專for 洗背既番梘 未知會唔會好有效<br />\n<br />\n暫時既結論：發覺啲方法好似都係舒緩多 點都係會生下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飲食呢bro"},{"pid":"0ea3e4902294b34b6ccfa84f5b79da9ad92ed2e7","tid":305841,"uid":30782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:51:26.000Z","msg":"我中學個陣係咁生，而家得d 印，但都搞到我唔敢去游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}